<item>
            <title>[MJAVADOC-211] create the report output directory if it doesn&apos;t exist</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MJAVADOC-211</link>
                <project id="12317529" key="MJAVADOC">Maven Javadoc Plugin (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;currently, the javadoc report relies on maven to have created the reporting base directory first. This need not be the case.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12804342">MJAVADOC-211</key>
            <summary>create the report output directory if it doesn&apos;t exist</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=21133&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
